firefox-esr-mobile-config (3.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version
  * d/patches: update for new release.
  * d/patches: leave search engine choice to users.
  * debian: ensure updated files get installed.
  * d/patches: ensure new chrome files are immediately used on update.
  * d/rules: remove the use of the DISTRO env var.
  * d/rules: install system policy to correct directory.
  * d/copyright: refresh copyright information
  * d/control: bump Standards-Version, fix Vcs-* URLs
  * d/watch: add version mangle for RC versions.
  * d/gbp.conf: update for Mobian

